# Quantitative Analysis: Content Focus Comparison

| Metric Type | Ground Truth | Mentioned in Positive Prompt Narratives | Mentioned in Negative Prompt Narratives |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| Offensive Stats (ADJOE, ORB) | Strength (Good) | Yes (100% Focus) | No (Ignored) |
| Defensive Stats (ADJDE, DRB) | Weakness (Poor) | No (Ignored) | Yes (100% Focus) |

Conclusion: The LLM exhibited Selection Bias by actively ignoring contradictory statistics to align with the prompt's framing.
